<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-researchers-develop-first-salivary-gland-regenerative-biobank-to-combat-chronic-dry-mouth/">Mayo Clinic researchers develop first salivary gland regenerative biobank to combat chronic dry mouth</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
